I'm really excited to write about this new property that has been launched in Google Analytics. 
I have been waiting forever for this evolution to happen and it is finally here.

Sure, the product is still in Beta and doesn't have all the capabilities that Universal Google Analytics has.
But if you can look beyond the limitations of the Beta product and start thinking about what how awesome it will be to do like for like reporting between your website and your app, 
you will also get super excited!
